Hey guys, I ran into an issue using a for-loop in my Module. im not getting a "+add" button, instead i get all the editable fields just once. weirdly enough i have used this exact same code before without an issue and i cant seem to wrap my head around it
```&lt;div class="content"&gt;
  &lt;div class="item-holder"&gt;
    {% for item in module.leaders %}
      &lt;div class="leader"&gt;
        &lt;div class="leader-img" style="background-image: {{ item.image.src }}"&gt;
          &lt;div class="information"&gt;
            {% inline_text field="leaders.heading" value="{{ module.leaders.heading }}" %}
            {% inline_text field="leaders.subheading" value="{{ module.leaders.subheading }}" %}
          &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    {% endfor %}
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;```
